      <title>法国 CAC 40 指数较 5 月高点下跌 10%，即将进入回调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/france-s-cac-40-drops-10-from-may-high-set-to-enter-correction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受开云集团 (Kering SA) 等重量级企业业绩令人失望以及政治动荡令投资者对国家财政状况感到担忧的影响，法国股市即将从 5 月份的纪录高位回调 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/france-s-cac-40-drops-10-from-may-high-set-to-enter-correction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:25:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合利华首席执行官舒马赫谈盈利、增长计划和中国业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-25/unilever-ceo-schumacher-on-earnings-growth-plan-china-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合利华首席执行官海因·舒马赫 (Hein Schumacher) 讨论了公司第二季度销售额增长低于预期的业绩。在接受彭博社 Lizzy Burden 采访时，他还谈到了联合利华的增长计划及其中国业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-25/unilever-ceo-schumacher-on-earnings-growth-plan-china-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:25:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日产和 Stellantis 踩下刹车，而雷诺则加速盈利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-25/nissan-stellantis-hit-the-brakes-while-renault-speeds-to-highest-ever-profitability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷诺报告称，上半年盈利创历史新高，得益于市场对更昂贵 SUV 的强劲需求。
与此同时，日产和 Stellantis 均报告了令人失望的收益。彭博社的 Craig Trudell 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-25/nissan-stellantis-hit-the-brakes-while-renault-speeds-to-highest-ever-profitability</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:25:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因业绩不佳而下跌，这是本季度最繁忙的一天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/european-stocks-slide-on-glum-earnings-in-season-s-busiest-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于开云集团 (Kering SA) 和雀巢公司 (Nestle SA) 等多家公司公布了令人失望的业绩，欧洲股市在企业财报季最繁忙的一天出现下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/european-stocks-slide-on-glum-earnings-in-season-s-busiest-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:14:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法航荷航因奥运会影响下调运力预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/air-france-klm-trims-capacity-outlook-amid-bigger-olympics-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于夏季奥运会期间游客避开巴黎，导致客运量下降幅度超出预期，法航荷航集团下调了全年运力预期，同时启动了冻结招聘和进一步削减成本的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/air-france-klm-trims-capacity-outlook-amid-bigger-olympics-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合利华股价因销量增长和盈利能力提高而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/unilever-turnaround-stumbles-as-quarterly-sales-disappoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着联合利华首席执行官海因·舒马赫 (Hein Schumacher) 的扭转策略开始取得一些进展，该公司上半年销量增加、盈利能力提升，股价随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/unilever-turnaround-stumbles-as-quarterly-sales-disappoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>炼油业务导致道达尔能源利润下降超预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/totalenergies-profit-drops-more-than-expected-on-gas-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道达尔能源公司公布第二季度利润降幅超预期，因欧洲和中东炼油利润率下降以及天然气价格下跌抵消了油价上涨的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/totalenergies-profit-drops-more-than-expected-on-gas-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:11:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stellantis 股价暴跌，盈利下降近一半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/stellantis-earnings-plunged-in-first-half-on-weak-us-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前，Stellantis NV 宣布将恢复销售旧款车型，并考虑降价以应对今年上半年销量的大幅下滑，此后该公司股价一度暴跌 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/stellantis-earnings-plunged-in-first-half-on-weak-us-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:30:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财富管理公司 Julius Baer 等待新首席执行官，利润下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/julius-baer-sees-client-inflows-accelerate-amid-benko-clean-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士宝盛集团有限公司 (Julius Baer Group Ltd.) 表示，尽管客户开始返还资金，但今年上半年利润仍然下降，这是去年 Signa 房地产丑闻后复苏不均衡的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/julius-baer-sees-client-inflows-accelerate-amid-benko-clean-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:22:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Benetton Scion 考虑出售意大利眼部护理公司 Sifi</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/benetton-scion-is-said-to-consider-sale-of-eye-care-firm-sifi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，由贝纳通家族继承人亚历山德罗·贝纳通 (Alessandro Benetton) 领导的私募股权公司在支持意大利眼部护理公司 Sifi 近十年后，正考虑出售该公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/benetton-scion-is-said-to-consider-sale-of-eye-care-firm-sifi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 16:52:58 GMT</pubDate>
